text: Strabomantidae is a family of frogs. They live in South America. These frogs do not have a free-living larval stage. They hatch directly into miniature "froglets". ==Systematics== ;Holoadeninae *Barycholos *Bryophryne *Euparkerella *Holoaden *Noblella *Psychrophrynella ;Strabomantinae *Atopophrynus *Dischidodactylus *Geobatrachus *Hypodactylus *Lynchius *Niceforonia *Oreobates *Phrynopus *Pristimantis *Strabomantis ==References== Category:Frogs of South America
title: Strabomantidae
